+--------+------+--------+------+
|      7 | Jack | Sphynx |    7 |
+--------+------+--------+------+
1 row in set (0.00 sec)

mysql> DELETE FROM cats WHERE cat_id=age;
Query OK, 1 row affected (0.01 sec)

mysql> SELECT * FROM cats WHERE cat_id=age;
Empty set (0.00 sec)

