|        1 | t-shirt    | white  | S          |        10 |
|        2 | t-shirt    | green  | S          |       200 |
|        3 | polo shirt | black  | M          |        10 |
|        4 | tank top   | blue   | S          |        50 |
|        5 | t-shirt    | pink   | S          |         0 |
|        6 | polo shirt | red    | M          |         5 |
|        7 | tank top   | white  | S          |       200 |
|        8 | tank top   | blue   | M          |        15 |
|        9 | polo shirt | purple | M          |        50 |
