Working with CONCAT
mysql> SELECT CONCAT(column,' ',anothercolumn) FROM table; <- space ot text between the quotes

mysql> SELECT
    -> CONCAT(author_fname,' ',author_lname)
	-> AS 'Full Name'
    -> FROM books;
